parameters.name: EffectiveOrNot
parameters.description:
Specifies whether the voucher takes effect. Valid values:

*   true: The voucher takes effect.
*   false: The voucher does not take effect.

parameters.name: ExpiryTimeEnd
parameters.description: The end time of the validity period of the voucher. Specify the parameter in the yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ format. Example: 2018-08-01T00:00:00Z.

parameters.name: ExpiryTimeStart
parameters.description: The start time of the validity period of the voucher. Specify the parameter in the yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ format. Example: 2018-08-01T00:00:00Z.
